Title: Worst of the Worst
Description:
Everything here suggests this is a well-coordinated effort. These slitherdrakes are almost like wild beasts. They will not stand a chance without our aid.

Find whoever is leading their operation and put an end to this.
ObjectivesText: Find and eliminate drakonid leading the poachers.
PortraitGiverText: As ruthless as he is heartless, Xymra's top priority is recapturing all of the slitherdrakes.
